{"tid":2135804,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個誤會 分開咗我哋3年","createTime":"2020-08-01T17:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T18:44:02.000Z","uid":340623,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a507075fca2bd54461a7c5e7552619489c26d4ab","tid":2135804,"uid":340623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T17:04:08.000Z","msg":"4年前識佢，我哋好曖昧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲一齊出嚟倒數，點知有一日佢突然間block曬我所有嘢<br />\n<br />\n直至上年暑假，我臨飛去英國讀書之前嘅一個月佢搵返我，佢話呢兩年幾嚟成日諗起我，佢話當時離開我嘅原因係見到有另一個女仔追我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（其實我唔鍾意追我嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我鍾意嘅係你），仲話佢唔係因為有另一條仔而走，因為我係不可取代<br />\n<br />\n基於&rdquo;ex搵返你唔等於佢仲鍾意你&rdquo;嘅原則，同埋我知道long d冇好結果，我聽咗就算，冇進一步行動<br />\n<br />\n呢大半年我reply佢Instagram story佢一係hea覆一係隔好耐先覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年佢入u喇，又靚女又有良知肯定好快畀人食咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔想知啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由見完佢到依家完咗sem我都好似有個心結解唔開， 好後悔冇問到<br />\n其實你有冇鍾意過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed630bc7581741e86644db9afe925fc22f64d46b","tid":2135804,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T17:08:14.000Z","msg":"條女被人射好射滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480c03f5f05b058f9ab21b01d06e21bed85a60f8","tid":2135804,"uid":340623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed630bc7581741e86644db9afe925fc22f64d46b","tid":2135804,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T17:08:14.000Z","msg":"條女被人射好射滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"我唔想知啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fe4faa21fa03b2999a37e71d3d8973f2cb5ba2","tid":2135804,"uid":120205,"like":0,"d